title: Ep. 113 - Democrats Criticize Kavanaugh For Being Angry? That's Insane
description:
The most insane narrative to come out of the Kavanaugh hearings is that Kavanaugh is an unfit judge because he was angry. Well, let's think about this. Why might a guy be angry at a bunch of smear merchants who have been trying to ruin his life, end his career, and destroy his family?
